ation=E2=80=99s founders, <strong>J. Tomilson </strong>and<strong> Janine H=
ill</strong>, with loans from galleries and a few works from his own person=
al collection. Needham recalled how Als showed up with artworks in his back=
pack the day before the show opened=E2=80=94like <strong>Larry Wolhandler</=
strong>=E2=80=99s small bronze bust of <strong>James Baldwin</strong>=E2=80=
