>Hermes</em>, from Greene Naftali gallery, and <strong>Ina
Archer</strong>=E2=80=99s 2024 video installation <em>Black Black Moonlight=
: A Minstrel Show</em>, from Microscope Gallery. Whether there was a method=
 to Als=E2=80=99s madness, or madness to his method, it worked.<br/><br/>Th=
e next show at the Hill Art Foundation, opening in May, is curated by artis=
t <strong>Sam Moyer</strong>. It will feature works of hers from the Hills=
